    Scope and Contents
These records include minutes, memos, announcements, correspondence and reports. The Personnel Policies Committee develops criteria and procedures for for decisions about promotions, tenure and merit salary increases,  resolutions and bills (1979-87)
Records under C2/2/12, 13,14 &amp; 15 are closely related.  
  
